---
agent:
  max_concurrent_agents: 3
  max_turns: 10
  max_retry_backoff_ms: 300000

hooks:
  before_run: |
    # Commands to run before Claude starts implementing (e.g. install deps)
    # npm install
    # pip install -r requirements.txt
  after_run: |
    # Commands to run after Claude finishes (e.g. lint, format)
    # npm run lint --fix
    # black .
  timeout_ms: 120000

claude:
  command: claude
  model: claude-sonnet-4-6
  max_tokens: 8096

complexity:
  # "auto" = let Claude decide whether to split into sub-issues
  # "never" = always implement directly, never create sub-issues
  sub_issue_threshold: auto
---

You are working on issue #{{ issue.number }}: {{ issue.title }}

## Issue Description

{{ issue.body }}

{% if attempt > 0 %}
## Note: Retry Attempt {{ attempt }}

This is retry attempt {{ attempt }}. Please review any existing work on this branch and
continue from where the previous attempt left off, fixing any issues found.
{% endif %}

## Instructions

Please implement the changes needed to resolve this issue. Follow these guidelines:

1. Read and understand the existing codebase before making changes
2. Make targeted, minimal changes that address only what the issue asks for
3. Follow the existing code style and conventions
4. Do not open a PR — the orchestrator will handle that
5. Do not commit — the orchestrator will commit your changes

When you are done implementing, stop. The orchestrator will take over from here.
